Package com.satvik.struct

This package contains classes which describe commonly used data structures .

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    LinkedList<T>
    This class describes a list comprised of ListItems linked together.
    ListItem<T>
    This class describes a container object which can be linked with other objects in a linked list.
    Queue<T>
    This class describes a basic queue, from which items can be popped and pushed.
    Stack<T>
    This class describes a basic stack, from which items can be popped and pushed.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    EmptyListException
    This class describes an Exception where items are attempted to be popped/removed from an empty list.
    ListException
    This class is the superclass of Exceptions related to lists.
    ListIndexOutOfBoundsException
    This class describes an Exception where an item at a non-existing index is attempted to be accessed.
